title: VERSUS SQUAD v1.26
description: Versus is a fast action twin-stick shooter from the creator of Nation Red. Create your own sandbox defense before doing battle with thousands of zombie mutants in fast-paced top down combat. Face up to a dozen bosses. Simultaneously.
